Package: data.tree
Type: Package
Title: General Purpose Hierarchical Data Structure
Version: 0.1.9
Date: 2015-08-01
Author: Christoph Glur
Maintainer: Christoph Glur <christoph.glur@ipub.com>
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Imports:
    R6, stringr
Suggests:
    testthat, 
    magrittr, 
    knitr, 
    ape, 
    networkD3, 
